28class TOutputMSL;
29
30typedef std::unordered_map<size_t, std::string> originalNamesMap;
31typedef std::unordered_map<std::string, size_t> samplerBindingMap;
32typedef std::unordered_map<std::string, size_t> textureBindingMap;
33typedef std::unordered_map<std::string, size_t> userUniformBufferBindingMap;
34typedef std::pair<size_t, size_t> uboBindingInfo;
35struct UBOBindingInfo
36{
37 size_t bindIndex = 0;
38 size_t arraySize = 0;
39};
40typedef std::unordered_map<std::string, UBOBindingInfo> uniformBufferBindingMap;
41
42class TranslatorMetalReflection
43{
44 public:
45 TranslatorMetalReflection():
46 hasUBOs(false), hasFlatInput(false) {}
47 ~TranslatorMetalReflection() {}
48
49 void addOriginalName(const size_t id, const std::string &name)
50 {
51 originalNames.insert({id, name});
52 }
53 void addSamplerBinding(const std::string &name, size_t samplerBinding)
54 {
55 samplerBindings.insert({name, samplerBinding});
56 }
57 void addTextureBinding(const std::string &name, size_t textureBinding)
58 {
59 textureBindings.insert({name, textureBinding});
60 }
61 void addUserUniformBufferBinding(const std::string &name, size_t userUniformBufferBinding)
62 {
63 userUniformBufferBindings.insert({name, userUniformBufferBinding});
64 }
65 void addUniformBufferBinding(const std::string &name, UBOBindingInfo bindingInfo)
66 {
67 uniformBufferBindings.insert({name, bindingInfo});
68 }
69 std::string getOriginalName(const size_t id) { return originalNames.at(id); }
70 samplerBindingMap getSamplerBindings() const { return samplerBindings; }
71 textureBindingMap getTextureBindings() const { return textureBindings; }
72 userUniformBufferBindingMap getUserUniformBufferBindings() const { return userUniformBufferBindings; }
73 uniformBufferBindingMap getUniformBufferBindings() const { return uniformBufferBindings; }
74 size_t getSamplerBinding(const std::string &name) const
75 {
76 auto it = samplerBindings.find(name);
77 if (it != samplerBindings.end())
78 {
79 return it->second;
80 }
81 //If we can't find a matching sampler, assert out on Debug, and return an invalid value on release.
82 ASSERT(0);
83 return std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max();
84 }
85 size_t getTextureBinding(const std::string &name) const
86 {
87 auto it = textureBindings.find(name);
88 if (it != textureBindings.end())
89 {
90 return it->second;
91 }
92 //If we can't find a matching texture, assert out on Debug, and return an invalid value on release.
93 ASSERT(0);
94 return std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max();
95 }
96 size_t getUserUniformBufferBinding(const std::string &name) const
97 {
98 auto it = userUniformBufferBindings.find(name);
99 if (it != userUniformBufferBindings.end())
100 {
101 return it->second;
102 }
103 //If we can't find a matching Uniform binding, assert out on Debug, and return an invalid value.
104 ASSERT(0);
105 return std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max();
106 }
107 UBOBindingInfo getUniformBufferBinding(const std::string &name) const
108 {
109 auto it = uniformBufferBindings.find(name);
110 if (it != uniformBufferBindings.end())
111 {
112 return it->second;
113 }
114 //If we can't find a matching UBO binding by name, assert out on Debug, and return an invalid value.
115 ASSERT(0);
116 return {.bindIndex = std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max(),
117 .arraySize = std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max()};
118 }
119 void reset()
120 {
121 hasUBOs = false;
122 hasFlatInput = false;
123 originalNames.clear();
124 samplerBindings.clear();
125 textureBindings.clear();
126 userUniformBufferBindings.clear();
127 uniformBufferBindings.clear();
128 }
129
130 bool hasUBOs = false;
131 bool hasFlatInput = false;
132
133 private:
134 originalNamesMap originalNames;
135 samplerBindingMap samplerBindings;
136 textureBindingMap textureBindings;
137 userUniformBufferBindingMap userUniformBufferBindings;
138 uniformBufferBindingMap uniformBufferBindings;
139};

141class TranslatorMetalDirect : public TCompiler
142{
143 public:
144 TranslatorMetalDirect(sh::GLenum type, ShShaderSpec spec, ShShaderOutput output);
145
146#ifdef ANGLE_ENABLE_METAL
147 TranslatorMetalDirect *getAsTranslatorMetalDirect() override { return this; }
148#endif
149
150 static const char *GetCoverageMaskEnabledConstName();
151 static const char *GetRasterizationDiscardEnabledConstName();
152
153 void enableEmulatedInstanceID(bool e) { mEmulatedInstanceID = e; }
154 TranslatorMetalReflection *getTranslatorMetalReflection() { return &translatorMetalReflection; }
155
156 protected:
157 bool translate(TIntermBlock *root,
158 ShCompileOptions compileOptions,
159 PerformanceDiagnostics *perfDiagnostics) override;
160
161 // Need to collect variables so that RemoveInactiveInterfaceVariables works.
162 bool shouldCollectVariables(ShCompileOptions compileOptions) override { return true; }
163
164 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD bool translateImpl(TIntermBlock &root, ShCompileOptions compileOptions);
165
166 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD bool shouldFlattenPragmaStdglInvariantAll() override;
167
168 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD bool transformDepthBeforeCorrection(TIntermBlock &root,
169 const TVariable &driverUniforms);
170 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD bool insertSampleMaskWritingLogic(TIntermBlock &root,
171 const TVariable &driverUniforms);
172 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD bool insertRasterizationDiscardLogic(TIntermBlock &root);
173
174 void createAdditionalGraphicsDriverUniformFields(std::vector<TField *> &fieldsOut);
175
176 ANGLE_NO_DISCARD TIntermSwizzle *getDriverUniformNegFlipYRef(
177 const TVariable &driverUniforms) const;
178
179 bool mEmulatedInstanceID = false;
180
181 TranslatorMetalReflection translatorMetalReflection = {};
182};
